  ```

* **Self-Monitoring**
 
  ```  
  pcf.{container.rep,cc,gorouter}.{cpu?percentage,memory?bytes,memory_bytes_quota,disk?bytes,disk_bytes_quota,disk_quota.bytes,memory_quota.bytes,requests.completed.counter,requests.CloudController.total}</code></td>
  
